OL,6,FAbout 100,000 civil servants are set to
OL,7,Fstrike on the day of the Spring Budget,
OL,8,Fthe Public and Commercial Services
OL,9,Funion (PCS) has announced.
OL,11,FIt comes after they staged a
OL,12,Fsimilar-scale walkout on 1 February
OL,13,Fthat caused disruption to a multitude
OL,14,Fof key services.
OL,16,FThis is the latest in a long list of
OL,17,Fstrikes that have affected everything
OL,18,Ffrom rail services and Royal Mail
OL,19,Fdeliveries to NHS nurses, ambulance
OL,20,Fdrivers and teachers since last summer.
